cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with generating human images based on appearance and pose information. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) for image generation. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper involves the use of AI techniques for image synthesis. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating images of human subjects. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper involves the generation of multimedia content (i.e. images) using machine learning techniques.
